    "description": "《废都物语重制版》是免费游戏《废都物语》的完全重制版本。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >融合了跑团要素的JRPG</h2></strong><br>致敬GameBook的表现形式，每个场景都以手绘地图的方式呈现。<br>融入了简易的跑团检定机制，为探索增加了趣味性和挑战性。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/c80fd26c0788d56f196a4926952ad76c.poster.avif?t=1757821566\" width=580 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/c80fd26c0788d56f196a4926952ad76c.webm?t=1757821566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/c80fd26c0788d56f196a4926952ad76c.mp4?t=1757821566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主题关卡考验重重</h2></strong><br>从童话般的森林到酷寒凶险的雪山，踏足丰富多彩的地貌，挑战不同体验的关卡。<br>收集线索，运用智慧和能力破解谜题，做出正确的抉择来攻克难关。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/de123681602441351ed80baed3fa8ce5.poster.avif?t=1757821566\" width=580 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/de123681602441351ed80baed3fa8ce5.webm?t=1757821566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/de123681602441351ed80baed3fa8ce5.mp4?t=1757821566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经典回合制战斗</h2></strong><br>数十种拥有独特机制的怪物，带来新鲜有趣的战斗体验。<br>不同伙伴的组合，技能与武器的搭配，以及对怪物行动的观察，都是取胜的重要条件。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/40b5d462039992c9a963202f9cfad7ea.poster.avif?t=1757821566\" width=580 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/40b5d462039992c9a963202f9cfad7ea.webm?t=1757821566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/40b5d462039992c9a963202f9cfad7ea.mp4?t=1757821566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冒险伙伴充实探索之旅</h2></strong><br>邂逅十余个具有不同能力，性格各异的伙伴。<br>他们会为你的冒险提供助力，增添乐趣。你可以走入他们的内心，了解那不为人知的过往。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/3ffcc19cca2df0762f5a122ee5092f70.poster.avif?t=1757821566\" width=580 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/3ffcc19cca2df0762f5a122ee5092f70.webm?t=1757821566\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185060/extras/3ffcc19cca2df0762f5a122ee5092f70.mp4?t=1757821566\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的多周目体验</h2></strong><br>主角拥有四种出身。通过选择不同出身代入不同的视角，才能拼凑出故事的全貌。<br>部分新内容只有通过多周目才可解锁，且埋有大量细节和彩蛋可供挖掘。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重制版革新点</h2></strong><br>· 全新的关卡体验，在保留核心主线的基础上，加入更丰富的互动内容和事件分支。<br>· 全新的技能体系，加入更丰富的技能搭配和战斗对策。<br>· 优化原作辅助系统和玩法，并引入自动存档、图鉴、成就等全新游戏系统。<br>· 世界观文本资料扩充，以及更多的同伴互动。<br>· 操作界面的全新升级。<br>· 更丰富的关卡剧情演出和战斗剧情演出。<br>· 原作美术素材高清化，以及更多全新美术资源绘制，提供更强代入感。<br>· 支持多种语言选择，支持手柄操作。",
